The @drduckco Journey Backpack.

New for 2022. One word comes to mind when we think about complications and problems that waterfowl hunters face: Water. We know that at some point either before, after or during the hunt, your gear could potentially and most likely will encounter water. We wanted to provide a solution to this problem. The end goal of The Journey Backpack was to create a bag, specifically for waterfowl hunters, that would provide maximum protection from water and the elements. We set out to develop a piece of gear that could without a doubt withstand the element of water, even if it was completely submerged... The result was a durable, 100% submersible backpack that features our signature customizable, adjustable integrated shelving system, integrated tree straps, and completely waterproof TIZIP® zippers. This is The Journey Backpack.

Presented by: @rusaoutdoors 
Video by: @ghostcat.co 

To shop the Journey Backpack, head over to @drduckco and click the link in the bio.

The @drduckco Oxbow Jacket.

Waterfowl hunting is known for its frigid temperatures and extreme weather conditions. Staying concealed, warm, and dry during the hunt is vital. The Oxbow Insulated Jacket is designed to keep you warm, comfortable, dry, and protected regardless of the elements. Built with PrimaLoft® Silver 100GM Insulation in the core and a thick, textured fleece lining in the hood and sleeves, this waterproof, breathable, insulated jacket will harness heat and keep you warm in the harshest conditions.The Oxbow is constructed from durable, yet flexible fabrics to allow maximum mobility and movement during the hunt. Waterfowl hunting, especially during late season hunts, entails wintery weather and frigid temperatures. The Oxbow jacket will allow you to focus less on your gear and the cold temperatures and more on The Journey.This is the Oxbow Insulated Jacket .

Presented by: @rusaoutdoors 
Film by: @ghostcat.co

The @drduckco Eufaula Non-Insulated Jacket.

Waterfowl hunting is known for frigid temperatures and extreme weather conditions. Staying concealed, warm, and dry during the hunt is vital. The Eufaula Jacket is designed to keep you warm, comfortable, dry, and protected regardless of the elements. The Eufaula Jacket is waterproof, breathable and non-insulated. The non-insulated design gives you the ability to customize your layering system throughout the season. The Eufaula is constructed from durable, yet flexible fabrics to allow maximum mobility and movement during the hunt. The jacket was built to act as an outer layer to your layering system, keeping you warm and protected from the elements, even in the harshest conditions. Waterfowl hunting, especially during late season hunts, entails frigid temperatures and wintry weather conditions. The Eufaula Jacket will harness heat and allow you to focus less on your gear and more on The Journey. This is the Eufaula Non-Insulated Jacket.

❌🦆GIVEAWAY❌🦆

It’s been a while since we did a giveaway! We are going to be doing an exclusive giveaway at our 4th Annual Season Kickoff Event — The event will take place on Saturday, October 14th from 6:30PM - 8:30PM. To enter the contest, shoot us a message letting us know that you’ll be there — At the event, we will have a QR code to scan and complete your entry for the giveaway. You must be present at the event to enter. We look forward to seeing everyone there!

❌Please note: We will not be contacting anyone about this giveaway through Instagram or Facebook messenger. Please be aware that there are fake/scam accounts  that will attempt to impersonate our account in order to gain your information — Please do not respond to any messages pertaining this giveaway. To enter the contest, you must be present at the event at our office and warehouse in Bixby, Oklahoma. The winner will be contacted in the following weeks after the event. If you have any questions, please contact us. Have a great day and Enjoy The Journey!
